description:
The strongest first love of the boy who gained the body and power of the witch ruling over the world!

Kuozaki Saika. The witch who continued to save the world facing apocalyptic events once in 300 hours, and the head of an academy that magicians attend. And the first love girl.

Following Saika's death, Kuga Mushiki, who inherited her body and power, will spend time as Saika in order remain order at her academy. And if he's careless and return to a man's body, he would need a kiss from a girl!?
